N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 333.16 - Purpose

State Regulations

Each college administrative conference shall act as an
advisory and consultative body to the chief administrative officer of the
college and it shall consider such matters as may be presented to it by its
presiding officer. Notes
